msg: When I contributed this test I did not realize that other XMLStreamReaders may interpret javax.xml.stream.isCoalescing differently.  So I divided the test into two new tests...one that uses a parser built om tree, and the other uses a programatically built tree.  The parser built test only has CDATA asserts iff the parser is woodstox.
